cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.MA 

The paper deals with the communication complexity of combinatorial auctions, which involves game theory (cs.GT) and algorithms/data structures (cs.DS). The use of interpolation mechanisms also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper applies its results to the study of mechanisms (cs.MA).
